  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/6cb7655d7aafb2fcbc8f8fadedba308b.avif?t=1764262169\" width=256 height=256 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/f3252c27cfd8093d25ecf157e7c07682.avif?t=1764262169\" width=256 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>1. Story of the Game</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kim Ttolttol, a young girl in her twenties and currently a college student, spends her days lazing around at home due to the recent college break.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As she crosses the street like any other day, she suddenly finds herself in a blank space amidst the sound of a truck horn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In front of the bewildered Kim Ttolttol, two gods appear, offering to send her home if she helps them...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>2. Gameplay</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/161f1be8239b548fd62da8dc5c5e9471.avif?t=1764262169\" width=600 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NewMe NuMe LuMe: Alien Wars is a 2D top-down action game where stages are cleared using movement, sliding, shooting, and melee attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The stages are structured with at least one boss and mid-boss, currently consisting of six stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/30014addac50bcd164aae467a3b46f69.avif?t=1764262169\" width=512 height=256 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/7867e1e2eabfdd46bc14fe68dc089cff.poster.avif?t=1764262169\" width=320 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/7867e1e2eabfdd46bc14fe68dc089cff.webm?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/7867e1e2eabfdd46bc14fe68dc089cff.mp4?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 11 weapon items in the stages to aid Kim Ttolttol's battles, which can be acquired and used to defeat enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/682f42a2f4219a9a4a6e90f0b4ee2b45.avif?t=1764262169\" width=512 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance health, movement speed, shooting, and melee attacks with money dropped when defeating enemies after clearing each stage, making subsequent gameplay smoother. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/f7f251bd4f0be3509c441b03964e221d.poster.avif?t=1764262169\" width=800 height=585 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/f7f251bd4f0be3509c441b03964e221d.webm?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>+ Additional Update</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/49c1b385aeff965fcd662384c0e93943.avif?t=1764262169\" width=512 height=325 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the basic 6 stages, three extra stages that continue the story after the main game have been added.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/7b3a06de5814d600bbc298b6a087b934.poster.avif?t=1764262169\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/7b3a06de5814d600bbc298b6a087b934.webm?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/7b3a06de5814d600bbc298b6a087b934.mp4?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the additional stages, two new player characters will appear alongside the main character, Kim Ttolttol!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/519ea000b5d089e9bee0c426c37a6c17.poster.avif?t=1764262169\" width=368 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/519ea000b5d089e9bee0c426c37a6c17.webm?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/519ea000b5d089e9bee0c426c37a6c17.mp4?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/cb44981241bffeb2850e1c4d551ad498.poster.avif?t=1764262169\" width=324 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/cb44981241bffeb2850e1c4d551ad498.webm?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/cb44981241bffeb2850e1c4d551ad498.mp4?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/8e0405aba7f0ec7f77772b6717ff13b9.poster.avif?t=1764262169\" width=364 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/8e0405aba7f0ec7f77772b6717ff13b9.webm?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/8e0405aba7f0ec7f77772b6717ff13b9.mp4?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These new characters have their own unique attack styles, different from Kim Ttolttol in the basic stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The additional stages will feature an epilogue to the basic stages, but you can play them even if you haven't cleared all the basic stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/084fedefeed91847e11b07619f176300.poster.avif?t=1764262169\" width=600 height=134 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/084fedefeed91847e11b07619f176300.webm?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/084fedefeed91847e11b07619f176300.mp4?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each stage features 6 to 10 different types of diverse enemies. Help Kim Ttolttol return home amidst their attacks! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/e2340fbc4324ae7d2336412024b8101c.poster.avif?t=1764262169\" width=600 height=247 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2855660/extras/e2340fbc4324ae7d2336412024b8101c.webm?t=1764262169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
